Kaminuza mpuza mahanga ya Rusizi  mu magambo y 'icyongereza ni  " Rusizi Interantional University (RUI)" ni kamunuza itanga ubumenyi [[Rwanda]] ikaba ihereye mu ntara y 'iburengeruzuba , akarere ka Rusizi ya kira abanyarwanda na abanyamahanga mu mashami yayo atandukanye , ikaba itanga impamyabumyenyi zitanduka harimo iyi kiciro cya mbere cya kaminuza ni zindi<ref>https://en.igihe.com/news/mineduc-rusizi-university-exchange-heightens</ref> .

== Amateka ==
Kamunuza mpuzamahanga ya Rusizi yatangiye mu mwaka wa bihumbi biri  na kumi ni ine (2014)  itangirana na amashami yayo atandukanye harimo ayubuvuzi bw' abantu  nu ubugeneni<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/amakuru-mu-rwanda/Rusizi-Urubyiruko-rwa-Rusizi-International-University-rurashimira-Leta-y-Ubumwe</ref>.

== Amasomo ==
Hari amasomo atangwa na kaminuza mpuzamahanga ya Rusizi akurikira:
