* Medicine & health.

== Ubuyobozi ==
Dr Gahutu Pascal ni wari umuyobozi wa kamuniza mpuza mahanga ya Rusizi <ref>https://en.igihe.com/education/gahutu-attacks-education-minister-over-rusizi</ref> mu ri 2017 

== Ibindi wamenya ==
Kamunuza mpuzamahanga ya Rusizi yigeze guhagarikwa mu mwaka w' ibihumbi bibiri na kumi ni itanu nyuma y 'isuzumwa ryari rimazwe gukorwa na minisiteri y uburezi mu [[Rwanda]] <ref>https://en.igihe.com/spip.php?page=mv2_article&id_article=36060</ref>.

